<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="consult-v">consult <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'sʌlt/    美 /kən'sʌlt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>请教；咨询；商量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>consult a doctor / lawyer / professor 
咨询医生/律师/教授</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should <strong>consult with</strong> your parents <strong>about</strong> your future plans. 
你应该与父母商量你的未来计划。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-refer-to">2.★ <strong>查阅；参考(refer to)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>consult a dictionary / map
查词典/地图</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>If you have any doubts about your health, you’d better <strong><em>_</em></strong> (咨询) your doctor at once.  （2015 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. consult  </p></div>